[Domestic cats present a risk because they can bring infected fleas into the house. Also you don't want an infected pet cat nuzzling and breathing into your mouth. But _Yersnia pestis_ responds well to antibiotics if taken early, and preferably prophylacticly if exposure is suspected. If you can it is worth watching and listening to the video clip in this report. - Mod.MHJ

